{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, PaymentSheet will accept all supported cards by Stripe."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can specify card brands PaymentSheet should block disallow or allow payment for by providing an array of those card brands."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: For Apple Pay, the list of supported card brands is determined by combining "},{"code":"StripeAPI.supportedPKPaymentNetworks()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"code":"StripeAPI.additionalEnabledApplePayNetworks","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and then applying the "},{"code":"cardBrandAcceptance","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" filter. This filtered list is then assigned to "},{"code":"PKPaymentRequest.supportedNetworks","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", ensuring that only the allowed card brands are available for Apple Pay transactions. Any "},{"code":"PKPaymentNetwork","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" that does not correspond to a "},{"code":"BrandCategory","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be blocked if you have specified an allow list, or will not be blocked if you have specified a disallow list."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: This is only a client-side solution."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: Card brand filtering is not currently supported by Link."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"cardBrandAcceptance"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payment-sheet\/documentation\/StripePaymentSheet\/PaymentSheet","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PaymentSheet","preciseIdentifier":"s:18StripePaymentSheet0bC0C"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payment-sheet\/docume